Package ohos.ivihardware.cluster.model

Class ClusterPropertyInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.ivihardware.cluster.model.ClusterPropertyInfo

  • public class ClusterPropertyInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    A wrapper class for Cluster signal values.

    The information includes the Cluster signal path, signal ID, node type, data type, and signal value, as well as whether the signal value can be set.

    Since:
    3
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Ivi.Cluster
